data.description: Welcome to this lovely townhome in the Winter Gardens neighborhood. Turnkey end-unit location by the pool in this charming complex with a new roof! 2 story with 2 bedrooms upstairs, & 1.5 baths. Inside has been upgraded in the kitchen (including newer stainless steel appliances), flooring, and bathrooms. Popcorn ceilings were also removed and recessed lighting added to living room and bedrooms! Comes with 1 covered parking space (the HOA can be contacted for an additional space for a small monthly fee). The $275/m HOA is one of the lowest in San Diego!
